- ğŸ” User Sign-Up & Login
- â˜ï¸ Upload files directly to S3 using pre-signed URLs
- ğŸ“‚ Store file metadata in DynamoDB
- ğŸ—‚ï¸ View uploaded files and download them anytime
- âš¡ Serverless backend (no servers needed)
- ğŸŒ Static frontend (HTML + JS) hosted on S3

