## ğŸ§© AWS Services Used

| Service     | Purpose                                    |
|-------------|--------------------------------------------|
| **S3**      | File storage & static website hosting      |
| **Lambda**  | Backend logic (auth, upload, list, download) |
| **API Gateway** | Expose Lambda as REST API endpoints   |
| **DynamoDB**| Store user data and file metadata          |

